findings.title: Owner can mint tokens at token launch
findings.description: The owner has the ability to mint tokens during the token's initial launch.

findings.title: Owner can-not lock or burn user assets
findings.description: The owner of the contract has unrestricted access to user assets and can potentially lock or burn them.

findings.title: Owner can-not stop or pause the contract
findings.description: The owner of the contract does not have the ability to stop or pause the contract.
